tabaseInitialization`.\n- The new test loads `DependsOnDatabaseInitializationDetector` implementations through Spring’s public `SpringFactoriesLoader`, then verifies that only beans annotated with `@DependsOnDatabaseInitialization` are detected.\n\nNo existing test logic was changed, and no reachability metadata or build files were modified.\n\nI did not run tests, per the instruction not to compile or run them locally.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_06490e8892739c18016a0d4879607481a09b9e85aeaae35057\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 2367, "output": 1233, "cacheRead": 37888, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 41488, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1779255402952, "responseId": "resp_06490e8892739c18016a0d486b827081a08a73390475808c41"}}
